#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an9.92"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.92:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.92:0.2"
msgid "9. Iddhipādavagga "
msgstr "9. Bases of Psychic Power "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 92. Cetasovinibandhasutta → vinibandhaiddhipādasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an9.92:0.3"
msgid "92. Cetasovinibandhasutta "
msgstr "92. Emotional Shackles "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an9.92:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, cetasovinibandhā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five emotional shackles. "

msgctxt "an9.92:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an9.92:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāmesu avītarāgo hoti … pe … "
msgstr "Firstly, a mendicant isn’t free of greed for sensual pleasures. … "

msgctxt "an9.92:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca cetasovinibandhā. "
msgstr "These are the five emotional shackles. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an9.92:2.1"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ cetasovinibandhānaṃ pahānāya ime cattāro iddhipādā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "To give up these five emotional shackles you should develop the four bases of psychic power. "

msgctxt "an9.92:2.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an9.92:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm, and active effort. "

msgctxt "an9.92:2.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … "
msgstr "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy, and active effort. "

msgctxt "an9.92:2.5"
msgid "cittasamādhi … "
msgstr "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to mental development, and active effort. "

msgctxt "an9.92:2.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. "
msgstr "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to inquiry, and active effort. "

msgctxt "an9.92:2.7"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ cetasovinibandhānaṃ pahānāya ime cattāro iddhipādā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "To give up these five emotional shackles you should develop these four bases of psychic power.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.92:2.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.92:2.9"
msgid "Iddhipādavaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an9.92:3.1"
msgid "Yatheva satipaṭṭhānā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an9.92:3.2"
msgid "padhānā caturopi ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an9.92:3.3"
msgid "Cattāro iddhipādā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an9.92:3.4"
msgid "tatheva sampayojayeti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
